 |archive-date = 2022-03-14
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20220314023730/https://www.durhamradionews.com/archives/107438
}}</ref>，但暫時編為407號公路的一部分。418號公路餘下介乎湯頓道和401號公路的路段則於2019年12月9日通車<ref name="CTV191209">{{cite news
 |title        = Final extension of Highway 407 now open to motorists
 |first        = Katherine
 |last         = DeClerq
 |work         = CTV News
 |date         = 2019-12-09
 |url          = https://toronto.ctvnews.ca/final-extension-of-highway-407-now-open-to-motorists-1.4721456
 |accessdate   = 2020-02-12
