 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref>，湯頓道以北的路段亦同時歸入418號公路。

2022年2月，省府宣布取消418號和412號公路收費，同年4月5日生效<ref name=remove>{{Cite press release |first = Ivana |last = Yelich |first2 = Dakota |last2 = Brasier |first3 = Simisola |last3 = Ikotun |url = https://news.ontario.ca/en/release/1001631/ontario-government-removing-tolls-on-highways-412-and-418 |title = Ontario Government Removing Tolls on Highways 412 and 418 |date = February 18, 2022 |publisher = Office of the Premier |access-date = February 18, 2022 |archive-date = 2022-05-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220507224017/https://news.ontario.ca/en/release/1001631/ontario-government-removing-tolls-on-highways-412-and-418 }}</ref>。

